Constructor Detail

circleRaster

public circleRaster()
Builds a raster surface based on an array of circles, produces the surface by using a density kernel based on the value of the circle. The mapextent is calculated from the circles.
Parameters:
circles[] - the array of circles
size - the size of the cells in the raster
data[] - the values of the circles
See Also:
